OL,3,CWhat is the Bab el-Mandeb Strait and
OL,4,Cwhy is it significant?
OL,6,FITV News understands that Iran's
OL,7,Fallies, the Houthis in Yemen, are
OL,8,Fthreatening to close a major trade
OL,9,Froute between Europe and Asia.
OL,11,FThere is real concern that an
OL,12,Fexpansion of the war will see the
OL,13,FHouthis engage and disrupt shipping
OL,14,Fthrough Bab el-Mandeb, which lies
OL,15,Fbetween Yemen and Djibouti, according
OL,16,Fto intelligence sources in the region.
OL,18,FWhat is the Bab el-Mandeb?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
