OL,3,CWhat is the Bab el-Mandeb Strait and
OL,4,Cwhy is it significant?
OL,6,FThe Bab el-Mandeb lies between Yemen
OL,7,Fand Djibouti at the southern end of
OL,8,Fthe Red Sea.
OL,10,FWhat is the strait's significance and
OL,11,Fwhat would disruption mean?
OL,13,FAt only 20 miles wide and 70 miles
OL,14,Flong, the Bab el-Mandeb geographically
OL,15,Fsmall, but vastly influential when it
OL,16,Fcomes to global affairs.
OL,18,FIt is a gateway for ships travelling
OL,19,Fbetween Europe, the Middle East, and
OL,20,FAsia via the Suez Canal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
