OL,3,CWhat is the Bab el-Mandeb Strait and
OL,4,Cwhy is it significant?
OL,6,FSeveral billion tons of cargo pass
OL,7,Fthrough the narrow waterway every
OL,8,Fyear, including crude oil and
OL,9,Fmanufactured goods.
OL,11,FWithout the Bab el-Mandeb being
OL,12,Foperational, vessels may be forced to
OL,13,Freroute.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
