OL,3,CWhat is the Bab el-Mandeb Strait and
OL,4,Cwhy is it significant?
OL,6,FAll the alternative shipping options,
OL,7,Fsuch as going around the Cape of Good
OL,8,FHope, would add significant time to
OL,9,Fthe cargo's journey.
OL,11,FAny such disruption of traffic would
OL,12,Fhave a near-immediate impact on the
OL,13,Favailability and cost of imports such
OL,14,Fas electronics, household goods,
OL,15,Fclothing, and toys, among other things.
OL,17,FIn terms of oil, the strait provides a
OL,18,Froute for oil and liquefied natural
OL,19,Fgas to Europe.
OL,21,FWho are the Houthis?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
