OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773191772
OL,3,CWhat is the Bab el-Mandeb Strait and
OL,4,Cwhy is it significant?
OL,6,FThe Houthis are a political-military
OL,7,Fmovement from northern Yemen, allies
OL,8,Fof Iran.
OL,10,FYemen controls the Bab el-Mandeb, and
OL,11,Fthe Houthis have, in previous years,
OL,12,Fused the strait strategically by
OL,13,Fthreatening shipping.
OL,15,FBlocking the route would allow the
OL,16,FHouthis to participate in indirect
OL,17,Fconfrontation, by disrupting
OL,18,Finternational shipping.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
